		<article class="entry social" id="post_20140527122507">
		<header class="articleHeader">
			<p class="pic"><img width="725" height="182" src="http://www.actzero.jp/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/eye-catch1.png" class="attachment-full wp-post-image" alt="eye-catch" /></p>
			<time datetime="2014-05-27" pubdate="pubdate">2014.05.27</time>
			<div class="tag"><a href="http://www.actzero.jp/tag/facebook/" rel="tag">Facebook</a><a href="http://www.actzero.jp/tag/sns/" rel="tag">SNS</a></div>
			<h1>最近のFacebookは情報を「守る」方針になってきた？</h1>
			<ul class="social">
				<li><script type="text/javascript" src="http://apis.google.com/js/plusone.js"> {lang: 'ja'}</script><g:plusone size="medium"></g:plusone></li>
				<li><a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-via="ActzeroInc" data-lang="ja" data-related="ActzeroInc">ツイート</a>
